		<div class="content">
			<div id="post-21525" class="post_box grt top" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">
				<div class="headline_area">
					<h1 class="headline" itemprop="name">Ray Kurzweil on the Singularity and Bringing Back the Dead</h1>
					<div class="byline small">
						<span class="post_author_intro">by</span> <span class="post_author" itemprop="author"><a href="https://www.singularityweblog.com/author/Socrates/" rel="nofollow">Socrates</a></span>
						<meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2012-07-18" />
						<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2012-07-18" />
						<span class="post_date_intro">on</span> <span class="post_date" title="2012-07-18">July 18, 2012</span>
<a rel="nofollow" class="num_comments_link" href="https://www.singularityweblog.com/ray-kurzweil-singularity/#disqus_thread">Comments</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="post_content" itemprop="articleBody">
<div class="pf-content"><p><img class="size-full wp-image-21204 alignleft" style="margin-top: 2px; margin-bottom: 2px;" title="Ray_Kurzweil_thumb" alt="" src="https://www.singularityweblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Ray_Kurzweil_thumb.jpg" width="150" height="123" />Just a few days ago I published <a title="Ray Kurzweil: As Humans and Computers Merge… Immortality?" href="https://www.singularityweblog.com/ray-kurzweil-pbs-immortality/">Ray Kurzweil&#8217;s interview for PBS</a> where he spoke about the merging of humans and computers and immortality. Below you can find three more videos from that interview which didn&#8217;t make it in the final cut. Still, those are all very interesting because Ray discusses the definition of the technological singularity, his desire to bring back his dead father, immortality and his aggressive regiment of supplementation.</p>
<p>Ray Kurzweil speaks about the technological singularity, the event horizon beyond which we cannot see, virtual reality, mind uploading and continuity of consciousness.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><object width="620" height="356" classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0" bgcolor="#000000"><param name="flashvars" value="width=620&amp;height=356&amp;video=2254816552&amp;player=viral&amp;end=0&amp;lr_admap=in:warnings:0;in:pbs:0" /><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="wmode" value="transparent" /><param name="src" value="http://dgjigvacl6ipj.cloudfront.net/media/swf/PBSPlayer.swf" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed width="620" height="356" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://dgjigvacl6ipj.cloudfront.net/media/swf/PBSPlayer.swf" flashvars="width=620&amp;height=356&amp;video=2254816552&amp;player=viral&amp;end=0&amp;lr_admap=in:warnings:0;in:pbs:0" allowFullScreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always" wmode="transparent" allowfullscreen="true" bgcolor="#000000" /></object></p>
<p>In the second video Ray talks about mortality, his father&#8217;s early death, his genetic inheritance of diabetes and cardio-vascular disease, bringing back his dead father and <a title="Turing Test" href="http://www.singularitysymposium.com/turing-test.html">the Turing Test</a>.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><object width="620" height="356" classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0" bgcolor="#000000"><param name="flashvars" value="width=620&amp;height=356&amp;video=2255442814&amp;player=viral&amp;end=0&amp;lr_admap=in:warnings:0;in:pbs:0" /><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="wmode" value="transparent" /><param name="src" value="http://dgjigvacl6ipj.cloudfront.net/media/swf/PBSPlayer.swf" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed width="620" height="356" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://dgjigvacl6ipj.cloudfront.net/media/swf/PBSPlayer.swf" flashvars="width=620&amp;height=356&amp;video=2255442814&amp;player=viral&amp;end=0&amp;lr_admap=in:warnings:0;in:pbs:0" allowFullScreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always" wmode="transparent" allowfullscreen="true" bgcolor="#000000" /></object></p>
<p>In the third video Kurzweil discusses his aggressive daily supplementation regimen aimed at sustaining optimal health and delaying ageing.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><object width="620" height="356" classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0" bgcolor="#000000"><param name="flashvars" value="width=620&amp;height=356&amp;video=2255223256&amp;player=viral&amp;end=0&amp;lr_admap=in:warnings:0;in:pbs:0" /><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="wmode" value="transparent" /><param name="src" value="http://dgjigvacl6ipj.cloudfront.net/media/swf/PBSPlayer.swf" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed width="620" height="356" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://dgjigvacl6ipj.cloudfront.net/media/swf/PBSPlayer.swf" flashvars="width=620&amp;height=356&amp;video=2255223256&amp;player=viral&amp;end=0&amp;lr_admap=in:warnings:0;in:pbs:0" allowFullScreen="true" allowscriptaccess="always" wmode="transparent" allowfullscreen="true" bgcolor="#000000" /></object></p>
